<div class="project">
<h3>LLM Comparison: Turkish Edition</h3>
<p><strong>What I did:</strong> Benchmarked ChatGPT, Gemini, Claude, and DeepSeek on Turkish language tasks. Evaluated fluency, tone, register accuracy, and cultural appropriateness using a 5-point rubric.</p>
<p><strong>Tools:</strong> ChatGPT, Gemini, Claude, DeepSeek, Google Sheets, Notion</p>
<p><strong>Result:</strong> Built a comparative evaluation framework now used as a reference for Turkish-language LLM assessment. Demonstrated how different models handle linguistic nuance and conversational flow.</p>
