</div>

<div class="project">
<h3>EN–TR Translation Error Analysis</h3>
<p><strong>What I did:</strong> Analyzed 50+ AI-generated translations from DeepL and Google Translate, identifying and categorizing errors in semantics, syntax, word order, pronoun drop, and cultural adaptation.</p>
<p><strong>Tools:</strong> DeepL, Google Translate, Excel, Notion</p>
<p><strong>Result:</strong> Created a structured error taxonomy used to evaluate and improve AI translation quality. Showcases linguistic precision and systematic QA skills.</p>
<a href="https://www.notion.so/EN-TR-Translation-Error-Analysis-A-Case-Study-on-AI-Outputs-30ccc2de1b31806f9e7ce6424d56b467" target="_blank">View Project →</a>
</div>

